SUMMARY:Bachateame
DESCRIPTION:Hello Bachata Lovers\, \nBachateame is back. Every first Friday. \nNow\, you know us\, we are dancers who created this event for dancers. We love Bachata and we are here to make it rain…Bachata music. \nOur crew of fantastic resident DJs\, and some guest DJs we will have in store\, are ready to play their best tunes for you. \nTell all your Bachata friends! \nDetails: \nLocation: 150 Elizabeth Street\, Sydney \nEntry is $20 cash at the door. The entry includes the class. (We have PayID as well if required but cash limits wait time and will get you on that dancefloor faster 🙂 \nClass time: 7.30 pm (Open Bachata Level – we will announce teachers closer to date)\nParty start time – 8.30 pm\nParty finish time – 1 am \nAny questions feel free to send us a message. \nSee you there! \nThe Bachateame Crew.
