SUMMARY:Latin Nights at Bulgarica – Salsa Class & Party
DESCRIPTION:💃 Are you ready for rhythm\, passion\, and lots of energy? 🔥\nEvery other Friday\, Bulgarica Cultural Center turns into the hottest spot for salsa lovers—with a beginner-friendly class and an unforgettable Latin party. \nWhen & Where\n📍 Venue: Bulgarica Cultural Center\, 1120 S Elmhurst Rd\, Mount Prospect\, IL 60056 \nSchedule (every other Friday):\n🕗 8:00 PM – Doors open\n🕺 8:15–9:15 PM – Salsa class (also suitable for complete beginners)\n🎶 9:15–11:45 PM – Latin Party with DJ Shinny \n🎟 Admission: $10\n✅ Includes the salsa class + the Latin party \nWho is the class for?\n❌ No partner needed\n❌ No prior experience required\n✔ Perfect for complete beginners\n✔ Great for dancers who want to refresh their steps \nWhat to expect?\n😄 A lesson with a smile: Step confidently into the magic of salsa—basic steps\, rhythm\, and leading/following\n🔥 Hot rhythms: After the class\, the dance floor is yours—DJ Shinny spins the best of salsa\, bachata\, merengue\, and more Latin favorites\n🤝 Friendly atmosphere: New connections\, great music\, and lots of dancing \nGood to know:\n👟 Shoes & clothing: Comfortable shoes (non-rubber soles if possible) and light\, loose clothing\n🚗 Parking: Free on-site parking\n📝 Registration: Not required—just arrive a bit earlier for quick on-site check-in \nCelebrate with us!\n🎂 Birthday or just a fun Friday night with friends—Latin Night is the perfect stage for great moments and unforgettable memories.\n💌 Message us if you’d like us to prepare a small surprise!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/latin-nights-at-bulgarica-salsa-class-party/2026-03-06/
LOCATION:Bulgarica Cultural Center\, 1120 S Elmhurst Rd\, Mount Prospect\, IL\, 60056\, United States
CATEGORIES:Chicago
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/296891_image_612135880_1529983379135400_6646739806602248253_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
